sequenceDiagram
    participant "Frontend SPA" as FrontendSPA
    participant "Backend API" as BackendAPI
    participant "PostgreSQL Database" as PostgreSQLDatabase

    activate BackendAPI
    FrontendSPA->>BackendAPI: 1. 1. GET /api/v1/projects/{projectId}/matching-vendors?limit=20&threshold=0.75
    BackendAPI-->>FrontendSPA: 8. 200 OK with List<RecommendedVendorDto>
    BackendAPI->>BackendAPI: 2. 2. [Controller] Invokes VendorMatchingService.FindMatchingVendorsAsync(projectId, searchParams)
    BackendAPI-->>BackendAPI: 7. Returns List<RecommendedVendorDto>

    note over BackendAPI: The returned DTO is mapped from the Vendor entity and includes the calculated similarity score. S...

    deactivate BackendAPI
